profile:
Steele Pools is based out of Oakville, ON.  We service Oakville, Burlington, Mississauga, Ancaster, Hamilton and Toronto.  We create custom swimming pools, water features, high end natural stonework, beautiful flagstone patios, outdoor kitchens, and more.   
We pride ourselves on using the highest quality products available and attention to even the smallest details in our workmanship.  
We specialize in Custom swimming pools and natural stonework.
We believe in quality over quantity and building a fantasy backyard oasis to last you and your family years to come.

profile:
Bud’s Spas and Pools is a second generation family run business. We’re involved in every aspect of the day-to-day operation and always available to answer your questions or resolve your concerns.

From the initial purchase and installation to maintenance requirements, Bud’s makes sure you have the best possible experience with your pool or hot tub.

Our staff of full-time and seasonal employee’s continues this experience year in and year out, building long standing relationships with you the customer.

Our ongoing customer satisfaction commitment continues today in two convenient retail store locations; Ancaster and Dundas.
